  "detailed_description": "You wake up alone, surrounded by wilderness; the only things keeping you sane are the voices in your head.  It becomes clear to you civil society is over but you can't seem to remember how.  In truth you can't seem to remember much of anything.  The only thing you can do is push forward.  After all, why argue with the strange voices in your head?<br><br>The corruption becomes you!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1491480/extras/d7eb926eff21c3711248d71782562d71.poster.avif?t=1621267919\" width=270 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1491480/extras/d7eb926eff21c3711248d71782562d71.webm?t=1621267919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1491480/extras/d7eb926eff21c3711248d71782562d71.mp4?t=1621267919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Kill zombies to gain crystals used to power up each time you die.<br></li><li> Defend points of interest from zombie hordes by crafting traps and towers<br></li><li> Search buildings and bunkers for valuable items and resources<br></li><li> Craft weapons and armor to better defend yourself from the hordes <br></li><li> Control and manipulate zombies as you become more corrupted<br></li><li> Sneak past traps and hide using stealth</li></ul>",
